# Role to Certification Mapping (Synthetic)

## Cloud Engineer
- **Primary Certification**: AZ-204 (Developing Solutions for Microsoft Azure)
- **Secondary Certifications**: AZ-305, AZ-400
- **Key Skills**: App Service, Functions, Storage, Security, DevOps

## DevOps Engineer
- **Primary Certification**: AZ-400 (Designing and Implementing Microsoft DevOps Solutions)
- **Secondary Certifications**: AZ-204, AZ-305
- **Key Skills**: CI/CD, Infrastructure as Code, Monitoring, GitHub Actions

## Data Engineer
- **Primary Certification**: DP-600 (Designing and Implementing Microsoft Azure Data Engineering Solutions)
- **Secondary Certifications**: DP-203, AZ-204, DP-900
- **Key Skills**: Data Lakehouse, Spark, Data Factory, Synapse, Real-time Analytics